If there a bug raised by calling addIdentifier(null)? I don't particularly like having to run the translation twice.
The other alternative is something like:
PatientIdentifier omrsIdentifier = identifierTranslator.toOpenmrsType(identifer);
if (omrsIdentifier != null) {
    currentPatient.addIdentifier(omrsIdentifier);
}

